</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>楊行密以其將張行周為<placeName>常州</placeName>制置使<pc>。</pc>閏月<pc>，</pc>孫儒遣劉建鋒攻拔<placeName>常州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>殺行周<pc>，</pc>遂圍<placeName>蘇州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
